<div class="nbunit" id="2Aug1928"><font color="red">2 August 1928</font> <i>BLHW</i> (to Harriet Weaver): I met John Drinkwater here &hellip; I must wait a little more before I write about <font face="wake">D</font>b. I seem to have little or no energy. </div>
